@startuml steering_input_to_mdps_state_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Steering Input To MDPS State Signal Flow\n(steering command + speed -> MDPS steering state / torque publish)

participant "Steering / vehicle inputs" as SteerCtx #F4F7FB
participant "MDPS\nsteering assist owner" as MDPS #E8F7E8
participant "Steering state bus" as SteerBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers / CLU / ADAS" as Obs #E8F0FE

== Steering Inputs ==

SteerCtx -> MDPS : steeringInput / steeringAngle\nvehicleSpeed\nmanualMode
MDPS -> MDPS : if steeringInput stale then\nsteeringInput = 0
MDPS -> MDPS : if vehicle stale then\nspeedNorm = 0
MDPS -> MDPS : in manual mode, derive steeringInput from Chassis::steeringAngle
MDPS -> MDPS : steeringAngleRaw = steeringInput * 30
MDPS -> MDPS : assistLevel = (speedNorm > 80) ? 1 : 2
MDPS -> MDPS : steeringTorque = steeringInput * 20
note right of MDPS
Representative gating inputs
- steeringInput / steeringAngle
- vehicleSpeed
- manualMode
end note

== MDPS Publish ==

MDPS -> SteerBus : frmSteeringStateCanMsg\nSteeringState
MDPS -> SteerBus : frmSteeringTorqueMsg\nSteeringTorque / SteeringAssistLv
MDPS -> SteerBus : frmEpsStateMsg\nEpsAssistState / EpsFaultState
note right of MDPS
Representative outputs
- SteeringState
- SteeringTorque
- SteeringAssistLv
- EpsAssistState
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

SteerBus -> Obs : steering state / torque readback

note over SteerCtx, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Steering command and speed context reach MDPS
2. MDPS derives raw steering angle, torque, and assist level
3. MDPS publishes steering state, torque, and EPS status
4. CLU, ADAS, and observers consume the effective steering-assist posture
end note

@enduml
